        Replaces the schema for a given parameter

        Parameters:

        paramName - String parameter name to look for
        newSchema - JsonObject containing the new schema
        removeExamples - whether examples should be removed. If the schema has been changed to an enum, this is no longer relevant

        JsonArray for the parameters, which can then be inserted into the path
